# OpenWrt Passwall2 Firmware for Linksys WRT3200ACM

This repository automatically builds OpenWrt 23.05.5 firmware with:

- LuCI web interface  
- Passwall2  
- Xray-core  
- Sing-box  
- Hysteria  
- dns2socks  
- ipset  

## How to build:

Go to **Actions** → select the workflow → click **Run workflow**.

After build finishes, download firmware from **Artifacts**.
